<p><strong></strong>Welcome to <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/events/290172758/">JavaScript Broth, Season 2</a></strong>. Eighteen Boston PHP members have signed up to participate in <strong>Season 2</strong>.</p>
<p>Only one participant has made the commitment to begin by posting a message in the <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53776625">Introduce Yourself</a></strong> discussion area. No participants have completed <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53776632">Sprint #1: Picking JS Apart</a></strong>.</p>
<p>If you are committed to improving your JavaScript skills, begin by gaining access to <strong><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/learning/hands-on-introduction-javascript">Hands-On Introduction: JavaScript</a></strong>. Then, proceed to the <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53776625">Introduce Yourself</a></strong> discussion area on the Boston PHP Meetup website.</p>
<p>The <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53776388">Master Discussion List</a></strong> contains links to the discussion areas for each of the three sprints, includingÂ <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53776632">Sprint #1: Picking JS Apart</a></strong> and <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53782405/">Sprint #2: Building JS from Scratch</a></strong>.</p>
<p>If you have any questions about how to proceed, please post a message in the <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53776625">Introduce Yourself</a></strong> discussion area.</p>
<p>Let's start stirring the broth.</p>
